OL,3,C'Complete and utter darkness' in
OL,4,Ctunnel system where Noah Donohoe found
OL,6,FA witness has told the inquest into
OL,7,FNoah Donohoe death that there was
OL,8,F"complete and utter darkness" in the
OL,9,Ftunnel system where the schoolboy's
OL,10,Fbody was found.
OL,12,FOwen McGivern, an official from the
OL,13,FDepartment for Infrastructure Rivers,
OL,14,Fwas also questioned at Belfast
OL,15,FCoroner's Court about access to the
OL,16,Fculvert system from the rear of houses
OL,17,Fin a north Belfast estate.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@]O]
