OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772557908
OL,3,C'Complete and utter darkness' in
OL,4,Ctunnel system where Noah Donohoe found
OL,6,FThe inquest into the death of the
OL,7,Fschoolboy at Belfast Coroner's Court,
OL,8,Fwhich is being heard with a jury, is
OL,9,Fnow into its sixth week.
OL,11,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,12,Fwas 14 when his body was found in a
OL,13,Fstorm drain tunnel in north Belfast in
OL,14,FJune 2020, six days after leaving home
OL,15,Fon his bike to meet friends in the
OL,16,FCavehill area of the city.
OL,18,FMr McGivern was questioned on Tuesday
OL,19,Fby Donal Lunny KC, who represents the
OL,20,FPSNI at the inquest, about lighting in
OL,21,Fthe tunnels.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772557908
OL,3,C'Complete and utter darkness' in
OL,4,Ctunnel system where Noah Donohoe found
OL,6,FHe told the court: "Once you go beyond
OL,7,Fthe first 10/15/20 metres of the
OL,8,Fculvert, it's black.
OL,10,F"It's not like black like night, where
OL,11,Fyou can see in your bedroom; you
OL,12,Fcouldn't see your hand in front of
OL,13,Fyour face.
OL,15,F"It is complete and utter darkness."
OL,17,FThe witness was then asked about the
OL,18,Frisks associated with gas in the
OL,19,Fculvert system. He said gas within the
OL,20,Ftunnels would only arise when it was
OL,21,F"agitated".
OL,26,@nD@TOUrD@AOUwD@AOUwD@dO]}D@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772557908
OL,3,C'Complete and utter darkness' in
OL,4,Ctunnel system where Noah Donohoe found
OL,6,FHe said: "I've been in it several
OL,7,Ftimes and the gas alarms never went
OL,8,Foff."
OL,10,FMr Lunny asked Mr McGivern about
OL,11,Fdesilting work which had begun in the
OL,12,Ftunnel network before Noah
OL,13,Fdisappeared, but the work had had to
OL,14,Fbe stopped.
OL,16,FMr McGivern said: "There were a couple
OL,17,Fof factors, Covid was a big factor.
OL,26,@nD@JOUpD@EO]xD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772557908
OL,3,C'Complete and utter darkness' in
OL,4,Ctunnel system where Noah Donohoe found
OL,6,F"But before that we took the material
OL,7,Faway, the material was identified as
OL,8,Fcontaminated so we then had to deal
OL,9,Fwith getting rid of contaminated
OL,10,Fmaterial and then Covid happened so we
OL,11,Fhad to pause and then unfortunately
OL,12,FNoah happened."
OL,14,FMalachy McGowan, representing Noah's
OL,15,Fmother Fiona Donohoe, told the court
OL,16,Fthat the jury had been on a site visit
OL,17,Fon Monday to the scene where Noah's
OL,18,Fbody had been found.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772557908
OL,3,C'Complete and utter darkness' in
OL,4,Ctunnel system where Noah Donohoe found
OL,6,FThe barrister said the grill over the
OL,7,Fculvert, which had been in place in
OL,8,FJune 2020, was a debris screen,
OL,9,Fintended to prevent larger branches
OL,10,Fpassing through, but wide enough to
OL,11,Fenable a person to pass through the
OL,12,Fbars.
OL,14,FThe witness confirmed this.
OL,16,FMr McGowan said the inquest had heard
OL,17,Fevidence from a number of local
OL,18,Fresidents about whether they could
OL,19,Faccess land near to the entry to the
OL,20,Fculvert system.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772557908
OL,3,C'Complete and utter darkness' in
OL,4,Ctunnel system where Noah Donohoe found
OL,6,FThe witness said the department
OL,7,Faccepted some local residents could
OL,8,Faccess the area from their back
OL,9,Fgardens.
OL,11,FMr McGowan asked how the department
OL,12,Fwould have known people could access
OL,13,Fthe area. Mr McGivern said the
OL,14,Fdepartment would have known this from
OL,15,Fspeaking to local residents.
OL,17,FHe was asked if the department was
OL,18,Faware that children would have visited
OL,19,Fthe area. The witness said: "I don't
OL,20,Fknow about that."
OL,26,@{D@]OU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772557908
OL,3,C'Complete and utter darkness' in
OL,4,Ctunnel system where Noah Donohoe found
OL,6,FThe barrister pointed to media reports
OL,7,Fafter Noah's body was found, which
OL,8,Fshowed a local parent raising concerns
OL,9,Fabout her children being able to
OL,10,Faccess the area of the culvert
OL,11,Fentrance.
OL,13,FHe added: "Would you accept that the
OL,14,Fbest and most appropriate way to
OL,15,Fidentify the real risk of children
OL,16,Fplaying at or near a culvert is to
OL,17,Fconsult with local residents?"
OL,19,FMr McGivern agreed.
OL,26,@uD@KOUyD@^O]
